            <div class="vuln-meta">
                <span class="meta-item"><strong>Endpoint:</strong> /login?next=, /register?next=</span>
                <span class="meta-item"><strong>Technique:</strong> Open redirect</span>
                <span class="meta-item"><strong>Impact:</strong> Phishing</span>
