            <div class="vuln-meta">
                <span class="meta-item"><strong>Endpoint:</strong> POST /checkout</span>
                <span class="meta-item"><strong>Payload:</strong> coupon_code=HALFOFF&amp;coupon_code=INVALID</span>
                <span class="meta-item"><strong>Impact:</strong> Coupon logic bypass, discount manipulation</span>
